videos.description: John Collins tries to drive the baseline for the bucket but Bam Adebayo swats it hard to the stands.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bam denies Collins hard at the rim) 2021/02/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bam denies Collins hard at the rim

videos.description: The Hawks come up with an offensive rebound, giving Rajon Rondo a chance for a triple to end the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Rondo somehow beats the buzzer with a 3) 2021/02/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rondo somehow beats the buzzer with a 3

videos.description: Gabe Vincent swipes the ball from Rajon Rondo, keeps it inbounds and flings it deep to Andre Iguodala, who rattles the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Vincent's steal leads to a slam by Iggy) 2021/02/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vincent's steal leads to a slam by Iggy

videos.description: Rajon Rondo fakes out Precious Achiuwa, but the rookie recovers to deny Rondo the jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Achiuwa won't allow Rondo to score down low) 2021/02/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Achiuwa won't allow Rondo to score down low

videos.description: Kendrick Nunn dishes the pass to the side and Precious Achiuwa powers up and smashes it down.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Achiuwa's slam get approval from the bench) 2021/02/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Achiuwa's slam get approval from the bench

videos.description: Clint Capela fights down low through several Heat defenders to tip in the rebound of his own missed shot.

videos.headline: Capela cleans up his own missed shot

videos.description: Trae Young drives down to the paint and draws a foul from Andre Iguodala as his circus shot falls.
